---
pagination:
  data: regions
  size: 1
  alias: region
permalink: /{{ region }}/isikud/
eleventyComputed:
  layout: "layouts/{{ region }}-layout.liquid"
---
<h1>Isikud</h1>

<p>Metsavenna elu algus ja lõpp ajateljel. Vajuta nimele, et näha isiku kohta rohkem infot.</p>

<div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-sm justify-center">
  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 py-1 px-3 bg-white rounded-full border border-gray-200">
    <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></span>
    <span class="text-gray-700">Tapetud</span>
  </span>
  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 py-1 px-3 bg-white rounded-full border border-gray-200">
    <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></span>
    <span class="text-gray-700">Arreteeritud</span>
  </span>
  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 py-1 px-3 bg-white rounded-full border border-gray-200">
    <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-400"></span>
    <span class="text-gray-700">Legaliseerus</span>
  </span>
  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 py-1 px-3 bg-white rounded-full border border-gray-200">
    <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gray-400"></span>
    <span class="text-gray-700">Muu/Teadmata</span>
  </span>
</div>

<div id="timeline-chart"></div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/apexcharts"></script>
<script src="/js/timeline-chart.js"></script>
<script>
  TimelineChart.init('timeline-chart', [
    {% for item in people.people %}
      {% if item.location == region %}
        {
          name: "{{ item.first_name }} {{ item.last_name }}",
          id_name: "{{ item.id_name }}",
          separation_date: "{{ item.separation_date }}",
          separation_end_date: "{{ item.separation_end_date }}",
          separation_end_cause: "{{ item.separation_end_cause }}"
        },
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  ], '{{ region }}');
</script>
